              <p>The data supporting the findings of this study are available within this article and its <a data-track="click" data-track-label="link" data-track-action="section anchor" href="/articles/s41557-025-01898-6#Sec26">Supplementary Information</a>. The raw data files in another format are available from the corresponding authors upon reasonable request. <a data-track="click" data-track-label="link" data-track-action="section anchor" href="/articles/s41557-025-01898-6#Sec27">Source data</a> are provided with this paper.</p>
